Invocation Name: asian american facts
des:
Interested in learning more about Asian Americans? Get an interesting fact about Asian Americans covering such topics as history, sports, entertainment, politics, and demographics.

The skill will prompt you to see if you would like another fact.

You can also ask the skill to repeat the last fact if you were too busy and missed what Alexa said. Just say:

"repeat that"
"please repeat that"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
